text: @UPSHelp I sat in my house all day yesterday and tracked my package about 4 times. Last time I tracked it said recipient was unavailable, which is a lie. Called customer service and she contacted the hub and told me someone would call me back within the hour. 5 hours later

@SABRONX Thank you for bringing this to our attention. I can only imagine just how frustrating this must be. I'd like to take a look into this on your behalf. Would you mind providing your first/last name, tracking number, delivery address and phone number via a DM please Thank you. ^KD https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
